race.comment: AUSSIE SAVANNAH (2) flew the lids from out wide with an impressive turn of foot before finishing second (19.62) and beaten 3.5 lengths over 350m at this track. Winning claims. ZOOM BOOM (1) boasts a strong record this journey here with three wins and three minors from eight tries. Placed last time (22.55) at Warrnambool in a Grade 5, finishing second and beaten a neck. Can feature with the right run. DONEGAL EXPRESS (5) was among the minors three back at this track then missed the frame the last two, but drawn box 5 this time where he has three wins. Rates a winning chance on best. CATHY'S DREAM (8) has strong credentials from this draw.
